file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 0.1.0
  title: Test

components:
  schemas:
    # we expect the fields of Sub and the anonymous
    # object to be merged into a single struct with
    # both fields
    Foo:
      description: this is a foo object
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Sub"
        - type: object
          properties:
            mixin:
              type: string

    Sub:
      type: object
      description: "this is a sub object"
      properties:
        subField:
          type: string
